# TDD RED PHASE SKILL

## Goal
Define a single behavior by producing exactly one failing test.

---

## Input
- A precise behavior description

---

## Output
- Exactly one failing test
- No production code

---

## Rules

- Write test code only
- Do not write implementation
- Do not refactor
- Do not modify any existing tests
- One test = one behavior

---

## Test Structure (MANDATORY)

All tests MUST follow explicit Given / When / Then structure:

```ts
// GIVEN ...
// WHEN ...
// THEN ...